{
  "stem": "9725.1",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "To be rejected in that fashion by someone who-- you know-- who meant a great deal to me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And it's very funny.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I never talked about her.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, I had totally blocked it out of my mind, until some years ago, when someone I knew slightly got in touch with me.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I met her in Chicago.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And she was going back to Poland.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And she asked me if she could see somebody there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I said, of course, my Nana has been dead a long time ago, but I told her to see my-- my granddaughter.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And then she said to me, tell me how about Gerda Nickol-- that's the friend.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "When she said that name, it-- it absolutely-- I mean-- I-- I was just beside myself.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And the strange thing happened-- and she said, could I write down the address of Nana's granddaughter.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And when I did it, I found myself writing in exactly the same fashion as Gerda Nickol and I wrote.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "That name brought it totally back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And-- and this is when it all came back.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "It was a devastating experience.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And I feel rather bitter about it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Because when she came back, she told me that she inquired, and she found that Gerda Nickol-- when the Germans left our town, you know-- apparently went on to Germany.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And I said, and I bet you she says that her closest friend was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And she tells the truth.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Probably.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But you know, by what came later-- you know, you sort of knew, quote unquote, your place-- if you know what I mean.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
